        <abstract> 
<p>Agassiz is strongly opposed to <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, but CD thinks K. E. von Baer may come out in support.</p>  
<p>Discusses the possibility of favourable monstrosities in the light of Theophilus Parsons’ essay ["On the origin of species", <hi rend="italic">Am. J. Sci.</hi> 2d ser. 30 (1860): 1–13].</p> 
